question: 年内
sourceMnemonic: <kanji>Inside</kanji> the <kanji>year</kanji> means <vocabulary>by the end of the year</vocabulary>. In other words, <vocabulary>before the end of this year</vocabulary>, or <vocabulary>within the year</vocabulary>.
sourceReadingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word, which usually means on'yomi readings from the kanji. If you know the readings of your kanji you'll know how to read this as well.
